[section#simd.complex.access
    [:en] Complex accessors
    [:zh_CN] 复数访问函数
]

[%@lib@member real[!basic_vec]]
[%@lib@member imag[!basic_vec]]
[codeblock:declaration]
constexpr [[redoc("*>")]]real-type real() const noexcept;
constexpr [[redoc("*>")]]real-type imag() const noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[:en] [`[*:c simd-complex]<basic_vec>] is modeled.
[:zh_CN] [`[*:c simd-complex]<basic_vec>] 得以构成。

[para:returns]
[:en] An object of type [*real-type] where the [$i^\text{th}] element is
initialized to the result of [`[^cmplx-func](operator`[`]([$i]))] for all [$i]
in the range [=range(0,size())], where [`[^cmplx-func]] is the corresponding
function from [?libheader complex].
[:zh_CN] 一个 [*real-type] 类型的对象，对于范围 [=range(0,size())] 中的每个 [$i]，
其第 [$i] 个元素以 [`[^cmplx-func](operator`[`]([$i]))] 初始化，
其中 [`[^cmplx-func]] 为 [?libheader complex] 中的对应函数。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member real[!basic_vec]]
[%@lib@member imag[!basic_vec]]
[codeblock:declaration]
constexpr void real(const [[redoc("*>")]]real-type v) noexcept;
constexpr void imag(const [[redoc("*>")]]real-type v) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[:en] [`[*:c simd-complex]<basic_vec>] is modeled.
[:zh_CN] [`[*:c simd-complex]<basic_vec>] 得以构成。

[para:effects]
[:en] Replaces each element of the [`basic_vec] object such that the [$i^\text{th}]
element is replaced with [`value_type(v`[[$i]`], operator`[`]([$i]).imag())]
or [`value_type(operator`[`]([$i]).real(), v`[[$i]`])] for [`real] and [`imag]
respectively, for all [$i] in the range [=range(0,size())].
[:zh_CN] 替换 [`basic_vec] 对象的每个元素，使得对于范围 [=range(0,size())] 中的
每个 [$i]，其第 [$i] 个元素的 [`real] 和 [`imag] 分别被替换为
[`value_type(v`[[$i]`], operator`[`]([$i]).imag())] 和
[`value_type(operator`[`]([$i]).real(), v`[[$i]`])]。
[div:end]
